latestIgtvVideos.title: Nykaa Naturals Hair Mask: Application and Results
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@nykaabeauty has launched its hair mask in two variants:
🍎Apple Cider Vinegar and Ginger hair mask
🧅Onion and fenugreek hair mask 
Steps:
👉Shampoo hair thoroughly 
👉Apply hair mask in small sections and emulsify well
👉Wait for 15-20 minutes 
👉Rinse with plain water and let your hair air dry

The mask is made from all natural ingredients, is SLS/SLES free, mineral oil free and phthalate free.

The mask has a creamy texture , it was easy to apply and rinse. 

My verdict: My main concern is dry and damaged hair. The mask had a great effect , after the mask treatment my hair felt smooth, tangle free , and healthy.
I will definitely recommend you to buy this mask.

Price: INR 599/200 ml
